{"lemma":"نِبْقٌ","slug":"نِبْقٌ","root":"ن.ب.ق","root_slug":"ن-ب-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ب-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n43808"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Rhamnus gen. et spp.","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Christ's thorn jujube (Ziziphus spina-christi); its produce, edible fruits and construction wood","tags":["collective"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"The vowel variation suggests a borrowing; it appears Egyptian in respect of the significance of its term nbs (“Christ's thorn jujube”) and سَنْط (sanṭ) and زَعْرُور (zaʕrūr) being of this origin, despite the last consonant mismatch, which is perhaps caused by the addition of another Egyptian word. In Classical Syriac once ܢܒܟܐ (nābəḵā) or ܢܒܩܐ (nābəqā) equated by Bar Hebraeus with ܟܢܪܐ (kənārā) and ܥܙܪܪܐ (ʿazrārē).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43808","headword_ar":"نَبِقٌ","root":"nbq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", properly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fruit of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lote-tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tree called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dawomN","text_ar":"دَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". The fruit so called is a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drupe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"resembling the crab. ―         -b2-  It seems to be also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A drupe"},{"kind":"text","text":"absolutely, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a drupe like that of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": see its dim., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nubayoqapN","text_ar":"نُبَيْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$okalu","text_ar":"اَشْكَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iroyaAnN","text_ar":"شِرْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}